<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Embrace the Beauty of Life</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/reflect.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>A Celebration of Life</h1>
        <p>Short, Sweet, and Beautiful Quotes to Inspire Your Day</p>
    </header>

    <main class="quotes-grid">
        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/sunrise.jpeg" alt="Sunrise">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Life is short, make it sweet."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/flower.jpeg" alt="Flowers">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Collect moments, not things."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/ocean.jpeg" alt="Ocean">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "The little things? The little moments? They aren't little."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/forest.jpeg" alt="Forest">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Bloom where you are planted."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/star.jpeg" alt="Stars">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Be the light in someone's darkness."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/coffee.jpeg" alt="Coffee">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Enjoy the simple pleasures."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/moutiens.jpeg" alt="Mountains">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Every day is a second chance."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/book.jpeg" alt="Books">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "Fill your life with experiences, not regrets."
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-card">
            <img src="/images/path.jpeg" alt="Path">
            <blockquote class="quote-text">
                "The journey itself is home."
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Inspiring Quotes</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>